issues.description:
When click on header elements to sort the data in the table it shows angularjs view
Found the problem, the data's disappearing because we load data with angularjs ng-repeat directive, but in order to sort the data by clicking on the table's header we need to load data with datatable API, specifically - fnAddData function, researching how to do that
